      "rationale": "CFD-predicted normalized index of hemolysis (NIH) compared quantitatively against bench measurements at all 5 operating points. Agreement is within ±15% for all points; mean absolute error 8.3%. Uncertainty in experimental measurements (expanded uncertainty k=2: ±6.1%) and model predictions (95th-percentile UQ band ±9.4%) are both accounted for in the comparison. Documented in ValidationResult vr/bench-hemolysis-5pt. Achieves Gradation 3."
