      "rationale": "Simulation setup was performed by a credentialed CFD engineer with 8 years of cardiovascular device simulation experience. A documented simulation plan (SP-2024-CPB-001) specifies all solver settings, boundary conditions, and post-processing procedures. An independent peer review of the simulation setup was conducted by a second senior engineer prior to production runs. No use errors were identified. Achieves Gradation 2."
